OL,5, Eight million people on means-tested   
OL,6, benefits will receive a cost-of-living 
OL,7, payment in February to help with high  
OL,8, bills - the last scheduled instalment. 
OL,10,FThe #299 payment will be made directly 
OL,11,Finto bank accounts, without the need to
OL,12,Fmake a claim, between 6 February and 22
OL,13,FFebruary.                              
OL,15,FThose on low incomes and receiving     
OL,16,Fbenefits such as universal credit are  
OL,17,Feligible, but should be wary of scams. 
OL,19,FA committee of MPs recently questioned 
OL,20,Fwhether the payments were sufficient.  
